              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22885901/" class="">附录：佛教智慧的真义(3)  </a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48469422/" class=" " title="Book.S">Book.S</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
